info.description: Place shaped pieces on board to fill in as many spaces as possible, but leaving designated scoring spaces open. Highest score wins.
info.helpText: Players take seats. Use blue deal face up button to show cards one at a time. After round, manually enter scores. Press square black button of next board to change boards.
